Description: Up for auction is PRS SE Custom 24 electric guitar, Fire Red Burst with Floyd Rose tremolo and SE gig bag, all in excellent clean condition with very light wear from playing and handling. I am the original owner and bought it new in 2018. This guitar was professionally set up by my LGS. The guitar has never been dropped or banged and it plays and sounds great. Comes with the original ES gig bag (no OHSC), tremolo bar and case candy. This guitar has not been gigged or otherwise played out and has no buckle rash, dents or dings. It has been stored in its bag in a smoke-free climate-controlled environment. Email me with any questions and good luck bidding!
